replies.body:
The communication was misleading (not precise, also including wrong statements, as others pointed out), and many got surprised. Therefore I would consider it as fair, to give another deadline to disentchant (ward-)skinshards for old values combined with a very clear official statement on it. 
To trick people out of fear about negative responses to system changes is not honest, and a poor reasoning. This has nothing to do with any judgments on the system changes itself.
So please compensate for the losses players received due to miscommunication.{{item:3301}}
